{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 45830862, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "PERI-2023-ANTI-COUNTERFEIT", "title": "Protection of the euro against counterfeiting", "publicationDateLong": 1675900800000, "callIdentifier": "PERI-2023-ANTI-COUNTERFEIT", "callTitle": "Protection of the euro against counterfeiting", "callccm2Id": 45830881, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43252433, "abbreviation": "PERI", "description": "Protection of the Euro against Counterfeiting Programme (PERICLES)"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 43252443, "abbreviation": "PERI-1-1", "description": "PERI-1-1"}], "topicMGAs": [], "tags": ["Falsification", "Fraud", "coinage", "Euro", "Forged", "Cash", "Banknotes", "Pericles", "Fraudulent", "Currency", "Coins", "Counterfeit", "Counterfeiting"], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "PERI-PJG PERI Project Grants", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43250350, "abbreviation": "PERI-AG", "description": "PERI Action Grant Budget-Based"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "15 February 2023", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "multiple cut-off", "description": "multiple cut-off"}, "deadlineDates": ["20 April 2023", "14 September 2023"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3480179": [{"action": "PERI-2023-ANTI-COUNTERFEIT - PERI-PJG PERI Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "15 February 2023", "deadlineModel": "multiple cut-off", "deadlineDates": ["20 April 2023", "14 September 2023"], "budgetYearMap": {"2023": 400000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2023"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">ExpectedOutcome</SPAN>:<p>The Pericles IV programme has the following <strong>general objective</strong>:</p><p>To prevent and combat counterfeiting and related fraud, preserve the integrity of the euro banknotes and coins, thus strengthening the trust of citizens and business in the genuineness of these banknotes and coins and therefore enhancing the trust in the Union's economy, while securing the sustainability of public finances.</p><p>The Pericles IV programme has the following <strong>specific objective</strong>:</p><p>To protect euro banknotes and coins against counterfeiting and related fraud, by supporting and supplementing the measures undertaken by the Member States and assisting the competent national and Union authorities in their efforts to develop among themselves and with the Commission a close and regular cooperation and an exchange of best practice, where appropriate including third countries and international organisations.</p>\n", "conditions": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">1.<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;bold\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Entities eligible for funding</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: eui-default, Arial, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">as described in section 6 of the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/peri/wp-call/2023/call-fiche_peri-2023-anti-counterfeit_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; Eligibility and admissibility conditions:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot